        "viz_pipeline": {
            "options": {
                "backgroundColor": "#252423",
                "fontColor": "#ec9960",
                "markdown": "## ⬡ AGENTIC PIPELINE — Fully Autonomous Threat Detection Loop\n\n**➊ FETCH** → OpenPhish (5m) · PhishTank (10m) · Email inbox (2m)  \n**➋ EXTRACT** → 31 features per URL: domain age · subdomain depth · brand impersonation · char repeats · digit ratios  \n**➌ SCORE** → Random Forest model (88.29% accuracy) outputs phishing probability 0–100%  \n**➍ DECIDE** → CRITICAL (>90% + brand) · HIGH (>75%) · MEDIUM (phish hints) · SAFE (legitimate)  \n**➎ ACT** → Auto-block CRITICAL+HIGH · Flag MEDIUM for SOC · Allow SAFE · Email alert on CRITICAL  \n**➏ INDEX** → Write to Splunk via HEC · Trigger real-time alert · Update dashboard live"
            },
            "type": "splunk.markdown"
        },
